<h2 style="color: #1f2937; margin-top: 0;">Reset your password</h2>

<p>Hi,</p>

<p>We received a request to reset the password for your Acer Coffee account.</p>

<p>You can reset your password using the button below.</p>

<div style="text-align: center; margin: 32px 0;">
  <%= link_to 'Reset password', edit_password_url(@resource, reset_password_token: @token), style: "display: inline-block; padding: 14px 28px; background-color: #8B4513; color: #ffffff; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 6px; font-weight: 600; font-size: 16px;" %>
</div>

<p>If you didn’t request this, you can safely ignore this email. Your password won’t change unless you use the link above.</p>

<p style="color: #6b7280; font-size: 14px;">This link will expire in 6 hours.</p>

<p style="margin-top: 24px;">—<br><strong>Acer Coffee</strong></p>
